name: am i alone?
description:
Amnesia makes me keep asking about self, and existence.
"Am I going to face it all by myself?"
"Am I Alone?"

"am I alone" is a zine created from a search for memories. Trying to figure out what had happened, but when I found the piece of memory he was looking for, he had doubts about its authenticity.

(This photo zine is the result of an online residency with @bertunas.zine)
